description: A water quality analysis of heavy metals (cadmium (Cd), chromium (Cr), copper (Cu), iron (Fe), nickel (Ni), lead (Pb) and zinc (Zn)) and dissolved/dispersed petroleum hydrocarbons levels (DDPHs) in the Godineau Swamp. For the project, “Preliminary Assessment of the Ecological Status of the Godineau Swamp, South Trinidad”.
name: TV_TTO_Trinidad_Godineau_Swamp_ecological_health_metals_DDPHs_2002
